# Local dev secrets for `wrangler dev`. Copy to `.dev.vars` and fill in.
# `.dev.vars` is gitignored; never commit real keys.

# Anthropic API key for the in-sandbox `claude` CLI. Injected into the sandbox
# env via the workspace `secrets` (never persisted to logs/snapshots).
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...

# Optional: an OAuth token instead of an API key (set one or the other).
# CLAUDE_CODE_OAUTH_TOKEN=

# DEV ONLY. Derive the bridge/tool-exec/preview host from the trigger request's
# host instead of PUBLIC_HOSTNAME, so a dev tunnel (`pnpm dev:tunnel`) works when
# you open the UI at the tunnel URL. The request `Host` is client-controlled and
# the per-run bearer token rides the derived URL, so NEVER set this in production.
# TRUST_REQUEST_HOST=1
